# Battleships

Console-based Battleship game written in Java.

## Features

- 10x10 game board
- Random preset ship layouts
- Missile counter system
- Hit and miss tracking
- Ship sinking detection
- Win/loss conditions
- Console interface

## Ship Types

| Ship        | Size |
|-------------|------|
| Destroyer   | 2    |
| Cruiser     | 3    |
| Battleship  | 4    |
| Carrier     | 5    |

## Symbols

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| *      | Hit     |
| !      | Miss    |

## Compile

```bash
javac BattleShipsGame.java